  Devoted to spreading the word of beloved Goddess Mitra, all her
Clerics are bestowed with a wide range of healing and defensive
powers that can protect and strengthen self and friend alike. They
are based in the one temple in the main city and from there, wage
the war against all manner of evil. For this purpose, Clerics receive
considerable fighting abilities, including the mighty guild hammer
that is said to be the essence of the cleric's own faith and the
power to devastate evil beings with a holy light.
  Clerics are also well known for their ability to provide various
useful services, including heals from afar, the removal of curses
and diseases and even death. Though it is by no means easy, those
who reach the pinnacle of their faith can bring the fallen back
from the dead.
  Clerics also share their faith with Mitra's pure warriors, her
Paladins. The two groups share much in common both in terms of
beliefs, as well as communication channels and even a common storage
facility. With their offensive and defensive powers combined, the
two make a mighty force against evil.
  If you like a guild that isn't built around hack and slash and the
thought of being able to heal, bless and strengthen yourself and 
others appeals to you, then talk a little more to an actual Cleric
of Mitra to find out more.
